What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Smart Lighting Market?

Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Smart Lighting Market

The smart lighting market is expected to witness market growth at a rate of 20.45% in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Data Bridge Market Research report on smart lighting market provides analysis and insights regarding the various factors expected to be prevalent throughout the forecast period while providing their impacts on the market's growth. The rise in the adoption for IoT devices and smart assistant platforms is escalating the growth of smart lighting market.

Smart Lighting is known to be one of the most significant lighting solutions for offering solution for both indoor and outdoor purposes with latest developed technology products including LEDs, luminaires, fluorescent bulbs and others.

Major factors that are expected to boost the growth of the smart lighting market in the forecast period are the constant arrival of the smart city projects in advancing countries. Furthermore, the enhanced adoption of standard protocols for lighting control systems is further anticipated to propel the growth of the smart lighting market. Moreover, the rise in the need for IoT-enabled lighting fixtures and smart lighting solutions is further estimated to cushion the growth of the smart lighting market. On the other hand, the rise in the early costs of smart lighting equipment and accessories is further projected to impede the growth of the smart lighting market in the timeline period.

In addition, the rise in the smart office and smart retail trends will further provide potential opportunities for the growth of the smart lighting market in the coming years. However, the disturbance in the smart lighting supply chain because of the COVID-19 might further challenge the growth of the smart lighting market in the near future.

